      "span_text": "Staining was done as previously described.  The fluorochrome-conjugated monoclonal antibodies used (purchased from BD BiosciencesPharmingen, San Diego, CA) were: fluoroscein isothiocyanate-conjugated anti-mouse CD4 and anti-mouse CD8, phycoerythrin-conjugated anti-CD44 and anti-CD45RB and biotin anti-CD62L. Biotin-conjugated antibodies were revealed by streptavidin-cychrome (Cy).",
